commitResults.messageBody:
Problem: The DiagnoseCommand accepted tags in all cases. This caused an issue for the findIllnessCommand when checking for matching tags as the illness tags are case-sensitive.

Solution: To make the find illness functionality case-insensitive, the illness tags are standardised to be in lower case.
